data.title: Contest T&C Document
data.text:
Offer Name: Click It Win It

Offer Summary: Visit Panasonic Store, Take a Demo, Share a selfie with prop and Win Couple Movie Ticket Voucher

Offer Duration: 8th August 2019 till 31st August 2019

TERMS AND CONDITIONS: This offer titled as “Click It Win It”. The offer shall remain valid from 8th Aug’2019 (“offer period”). Offer valid at select locations, on purchase from Exclusive channel outlets only. Offer valid till stocks/ lasts within offer period. The offers are at the sole discretion of Panasonic management and can be withdrawn at any given point in time without any prior notice. The images are for representation purpose only and the actual products may vary. All disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts at New Delhi only. Prices wherever mentioned are inclusive of all taxes.

ELIGIBILITY:

(a) Any person who is citizen/resident of India and is 18 years of age or above: (1) Who is not barred by any legal disability: and (2) Who is not suffering any mental disability: (3) Who has never been conducted in any criminal case: and (4) Who is a PAN card holder: (5) The purchases made from Panasonic Brand Stores/ Panasonic Exclusive Stores Panasonic Authorized Dealers will only be considered eligible and valid purchase for this Offer.

T&Cs:

This contest is conducted by Panasonic India Private Limited hereafter to be referred as (“Organizer”/ “Panasonic”). The contest is applicable in all Indian metropolitan cities for residents of India only except in the state of Tamil Nadu.

The Participants agree that they are sharing their personal information out of their own free will and shall not hold Panasonic responsible for any misuse or any other use of the information whatsoever. Amongst all the entries received, Panasonic India Private Limited will decide the winner of contest. Winners will be decided as per Panasonic India Private Limited sole discretion, the criteria for winner selection won’t be shared with any participant in any case whatsoever. All decisions of Panasonic regarding running / process / results, of the Contest, data selection shall be final and binding on the Participants under this Contest. No appeals and solicitations will be entertained in this regard. Organizer reserves the right at any time, without prior notice, to add or vary all or any of these terms and conditions or to replace, wholly or in part this Contest or to withdraw it completely. Organizer reserves the right, at its own discretion and without cause, to disqualify any individual from participating in the Contest. Organizer also reserves the right at its own discretion to withhold/forfeit any Prize won by Participants suspected of violating these Terms and Conditions. Any disputes arising from this Contest shall be subject to exclusive jurisdiction of Courts at New Delhi only.

The Contest is just for engaging customers or prospects and there is neither any relation to any sort of gambling, lottery etc. nor Organizer/ its agency has any intention of harming any sentiments of society/ persons who do not qualify. Contest shall be void in any state where prohibited by law. In such case, Organizer shall not be liable to provide any free gift to the Participant on any account.

The Participant hereby agrees and undertakes to hold harmless and indemnify Organizer and/ or any of their group entities or affiliates, their respective directors, officers, employees, agents, vendors, for or liable for, any actions, claims, demands, losses, damages, costs, charges and expenses, either direct or remote that they may/might have suffered, sustained or incurred, or claim to suffer, sustain or incur, by way of and/or on account of the any act or omission of the Participant. Participant agrees that Organizer shall not be liable for any claims, costs, injuries, losses or damages of any kind arising out of or in connection with the Contest or with the acceptance, possessions, or use of any prize. Any and all applicable taxes as may be applicable from time to time in relation to the Contest or acceptance of the free Gifts shall be borne by the Participant. Organizer shall not in any manner be liable or responsible for the same.

Organizer’s social media policy is applicable. This activity is in no way sponsored, endorsed or administered by, or associated with Facebook and Instagram.

Criteria’s to Qualify the Contest & get Couple Movie Ticket Voucher Code:

1. Participants need to visit any Panasonic Exclusive Outlet (BS/ P4/ P2 – list attached for reference), take a Demo of any Panasonic product, share a selfie on Facebook/ Instagram account in order to qualify.

2. Participants must include #FreedomToWin and tag @PanasonicIndia in their entry. Without the above-mentioned hashtag & tagging of Panasonic, the entry will be disqualified.

3. The user/ participant needs to send the screenshot of his Facebook/ Instagram post along with any one valid photo ID proof (Ex - Voter ID, Driving Licence, Aadhar Card or Passport) on the E-mail ID - freedomtoein.panasonic@gmail.com.

4. Entries will be scrutinized on a daily basis and the entries received will be validated first.

5. The Contest is valid for Indian Residents, except employees and family members of Organizer and its affiliates / associate / subsidiary companies and their suppliers, advertising agencies and event management companies (“Participant”).

6. Only first 1000 qualified winners will be eligible to win couple movie voucher.

7. The winner need to redeem couple movie ticket voucher as per below process.

8. The participation in the Contest is voluntary.

9. Any Participant who manipulates the Contest in any manner shall be liable for disqualification at the sole discretion of Organizer.

10. The entries will be screened for defamatory content/language.

11. Entries received after closing time will not be processed. Incomplete/ incorrect entries from third party agents or bulk entries will not be eligible.

T&C for Couple Movie Ticket Redemption

1. The voucher (received through customer messenger) entitles the user to a couple movie ticket at participating cinemas from Mon-Thursday all shows, Fri, Sat & Sun for shows till 4PM.

2. To register visit www.cinerewardz.com[AK1] [NK2] , enter e-voucher code, fill up the form and click on submit to receive the authentication number. To book, click on the booking request tab for movie, enter the authentication number, fill up the required details and click ‘submit’. You will receive a call from concierge 24 hours prior to the booking request date confirming one of the available choices and an e-mail / SMS confirmation will be sent.

3. If your mobile number is registered under the “Do Not Disturb” registry, you will not receive any Auto-Registration response. However, you will receive the Authentication Number via e-mail.

4. Bookings will be confirmed only from Monday to Friday. All booking requests submitted on Saturday and Sunday will be attended on the subsequent Monday.

5. A minimum of 2 days and a maximum of 7 days advance notice are mandatory to make a booking.

6. Walk-in customers without prior reservation will not be entertained at the venue.

7. To avail the offer, customer need to show the SMS confirmation or a print out of the e-ticket at the venue.

8. Once booked, the ticket cannot be cancelled or rescheduled.

9. For any queries, please email to nidhi.makwana@rewardport.in/

bhavna@rewardport.in

10. This offer is not available to employees of Panasonic India Ltd., WAT Consult and REWARDPORT CORPORATE SOLUTONSPVT. LTD., its clients or agencies and their immediate families.

11. This offer is not exchangeable for “cash” or for sale.

12. This offer is applicable only on 2D movies and excludes 3D movies, Imax and other special screenings.

13. Redemption of ticket is subject to availability of seats.

14. Offer excludes Public Holidays and bank holidays.

15. Film classification rules apply, and identification may be required.

16. The list of participating venues remains subject to change.

17. Participating venues reserve the right to vary the timings and Offer availability. Some venues have restricted timings on the availability of the Offer. Customers are recommended to call the concierge in advance to check the exact terms of the Offer. Concierge line +022 26748000, 40270000. Lines open from Monday to Friday between 10:30 AM and 5:30 PM, except public and bank holidays.

18. Only one voucher per booking will be entertained. Multiple vouchers cannot be booked. Only one voucher may be used per person, per household, per mobile no, per venue, per booking group (group is defined as more than one person accompanying the voucher holder).

19. The offer is based on advance bookings only and is subject to promotional availability.

20. The voucher is valid for best available silver class seats and not valid for special screenings, paid preview, premier and gold class seats.

21. The “How to Use” instructions form a part of these Terms & Conditions.

22. Any costs associated with entering the promotion, including accessing the promotional website, are the responsibility of each entrant.

23. The usage of this Voucher (“Voucher”) is incumbent upon the terms & conditions to be followed by the Voucher holder/purchaser. Such conditions need to be followed by the voucher holder/ purchaser. Customers must comply with all the Terms & Conditions herein before claiming the Offer. Panasonic has the right to reject any claims that do not conform to the Terms & Conditions.

24. If the Promoter has already emailed, or sent by SMS, an entrant’s Movie ticket voucher code to the email address submitted on entry, the Promoter will not re-send the Movie ticket e-voucher code to any new or corrected email address or phone number nominated by the entrant

25. If this promotion is interfered with in any way or is not capable of being conducted as reasonably anticipated due to any reason beyond the reasonable control of the Promoter, including but not limited to technical difficulties, unauthorized intervention or fraud, the Promoter reserves the right, in its sole discretion, to the fullest extent permitted by law (a) to invalidate any customer; or (b) subject to any written directions from a regulatory authority, to modify, suspend, terminate or cancel the promotion, as appropriate

26. Panasonic is not responsible for any problems or technical malfunction of any telephone or network or lines, servers or providers, computer equipment, software, technical problems or traffic congestion on a mobile network, or any combination thereof, or any other technical failures including any damage to entrant's or any other person's mobile handset or computer related to, or resulting from, participation in this promotion or the downloading of any materials related to this promotion.

27. Panasonic reserves the right to change the terms and conditions of this Offer, including extending, withdrawing, or discontinuing the same without notice, without assigning any reason, at their sole discretion and without any liability.

28. Agency and Panasonic shall not be liable in any manner for any cost or expense incurred for the purpose of redemption of the Offer and / or

29. If for any reason this promotion is not capable of running as planned because of infection by computer virus, bugs, tampering, unauthorized intervention, technical failures or any other causes beyond the reasonable control of the Promoter which corrupt or affect the administration, security, fairness, integrity or proper conduct of this promotion, the Promoter reserves the right in its sole discretion to cancel, terminate, modify or suspend the promotion, subject to any written directions made under applicable State or Territory legislation.

30. Caution: any attempt to deliberately damage the Promoter's promotional website or the information on the website, to cause malicious damage or interference with the normal functioning of the website, or to otherwise undermine the legitimate operation of this promotion may be a violation of criminal and civil laws and should such an attempt be made, whether successful or not, the Promoter reserves the right to seek damages to the fullest extent permitted by law. If the Promoter suffers loss or incurs any costs in connection with any breach of these Terms or any other legal obligation by an entrant, the entrant agrees to indemnify the promoter for those losses, damages and costs.

31. The cinema voucher has no monetary value, is non-transferable and cannot be used in conjunction with any other promotional offer.

32. The cinema manager’s decision is final and standard cinema rules apply.

33. The holder of this offer is not entitled to any preferential right over other cinema patrons.

34. Panasonic India Ltd., its agents and distributors accept no responsibility, financial or otherwise for the misuse of the voucher, and are not liable for any personal loss or injury at featured venues, and cannot be held responsible for any dissatisfaction concerning quality or availability of featured venues.

35. Under this Offer, the vouchers are being offered, directly by Agency, Panasonic India Ltd., is not responsible for the same.

36. Panasonic India Ltd. does not endorse the quality of any of the products or services being offered as vouchers under the Offer. Any complaints or queries pertaining to the same would have to be taken up directly with the REWARDPORT CORPORATE SOLUTONSPVT. LTD. of such a product or service.

37. Panasonic reserves the right, at any stage, to disqualify any Customer without notice, including but not limited to, if Panasonic believes in its sole and unfettered discretion that such Customer violates any law or regulation for the time being in force, infringes upon any third party right or otherwise does not comply with these Terms and Conditions. Panasonic’ decision in this respect will be final and binding on the Customers

38. REWARDPORT CORPORATE SOLUTONSPVT. LTD. is acting as an executing agency for this promotional offer and holds no legal and financial liability on unclaimed offers, incentives, vouchers, etc. beyond the applicable period of the promotional offer.

39. Panasonic reserves the right to change / modify / withdraw / suspend / cancel this offer at any time at its sole discretion without giving any notice and without assigning any reason.

40. The decision of the promoter is final and binding

41. 43. Panasonic shall in no way be held responsible or liable for any non-compliance of any of the conditions laid down under these Terms and Conditions.

42. All decisions of Panasonic regarding the Offer shall be final and binding. Any dispute, difference, proceedings or claim of any nature in connection with the Offer shall be subject the exclusive jurisdiction of the Courts in Delhi

43. Customers/ Company shall at all times fully indemnify and hold harmless Panasonic, their officers, directors, agents, and employees, associate companies from any and all costs, losses, claims, demands, damages and liabilities ,actions including costs and reasonable attorneys' fees, made by any third party and/or penalty imposed due to and/or arising out of breach of the Terms & Conditions and/or violation of any law, rules or regulations and/or the rights of a third party and/or the infringement by Customers/ Company including, without limitation, copyright and trademark infringement, obscene and/or indecent postings, and on-line defamation, and/or any third party or of any intellectual property and/or other right of any person and/or entity.

44. Panasonic reserves the right to, terminate, modify or extend this Offer, at any time at its absolute discretion, without assigning any reason. Decision of Panasonic will be final and binding regarding this Offer and prizes. Panasonic reserves the right to alter the Offer, add or remove the products /Offer without any prior notice. Any clarification on the Offer shall be made within 7 days of the receipt of the Offer. No query or correspondence shall be entertained after the expiry of the same. All decisions of Panasonic regarding running / process / redemption etc of the Offer, shall be final and binding on the Customers under this Offer. No appeals and solicitations will be entertained in this regard

45. By participating in this Offer, Customers/ Company hereby affirms and declares that the information submitted for this Offer is true and agrees to keep Panasonic indemnified against any claims, losses, damages, expenses (Including attorney’s fees) raised by any third party/person. Panasonic shall not go into the merits of such claim by the third party/person but shall deem that such information is infringed and would reserve its right to proceed in manner as per legal remedies available.

46. Promoter/ Agency: REWARDPORT CORPORATE SOLUTONSPVT. LTD

47. Last date to register: 20th September, 2019. Offer validity: 30th Novemeber, 2019.

48. The Offer is available till stock lasts.

How To Redeem

1. Customer visits any Panasonic Exclusive outlet & take product demonstration of any Panasonic product.

2. Clicks Selfie with the Prop, Mention #FreedomToWin and Post on their Facebook or Instagram account by Tagging @Panasonicindia Facebook/Instagram page.

3. The user needs to send the screenshot of his Facebook/ Instagram post along with any one valid photo ID proof (Ex - Voter ID, Driving Licence, Aadhar Card or Passport) on the E-mail ID - freedomtoein.panasonic@gmail.com

4. Qualified entries/ winners will receive Couple Movie Ticket voucher code & website link through above E-mail ID within 3-4 days from date of sharing documents.

4. Post receiving the voucher code, users visit & register at www.cinerewardz.com, by entering voucher code and filling up the form and click Submit.

5. On completion of registration, customer will receive an Email /sms providing you with the Authentication Number Instantly.

6. Once Authentication number received, click on the Booking Request Tab.

7. Enter Authentication number that you have received via SMS /Email, fill up the required details and click "Submit".

8. Our representative will call you 24 hours to 48 hours after the Booking request and confirm one of the available choices. In case of non-availability, we will provide you with alternate options for confirmation. For any queries, call our concierge line +022 26748000, 40270000. Lines open from Monday to Friday between 10:30 AM and 5:30 PM, except public and bank holidays.

9. To redeem the experience, show the Print out/ (E-ticket)/ SMS at the venue.

10. The voucher entitles the user to a couple movie ticket at participating cinemas from Mon- Thursday all shows, Fri, Sat & Sun for shows till 4PM. Offer is applicable only on 2D movies and excludes 3D movies, Imax and other special screenings. Voucher is valid for best available silver class seats and not valid for special screenings, paid preview, premier and gold class seats.

11. Last date to register: 20th September, 2019. Offer validity: 30th November,2019.

12. For any queries write to us on nidhi.makwana@rewardport.in / bhavna@rewardport.in

Poster T&C:

The offer “Click It Win It” is valid from 8th August 2019 – 31st August 2019. Last date to register: 20th September, 2019. Offer validity: 30th November, 2019.

Participants need to visit any Panasonic Exclusive Outlet (BS/ P4/ P2) take a Demo of any Panasonic product, click a selfie while taking demo share selfie on their Facebook/ Instagram account. Participants must include #FreedomToWin and tag @PanasonicIndia in their entry in order to qualify. Without the above-mentioned hashtag & tagging of Panasonic, the entry will be disqualified. First 1000 qualified winners will only get couple movie voucher. Only one voucher per booking per person will be entertained.

The contest is at the sole discretion of Panasonic management and can be withdrawn at any given point in time without any prior notice. The images are for representation purpose only and the actual products may vary. All disputes shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts at New Delhi only. For detailed T&C, please visit www.panasonicmovie.promoredemption.com.
